@NODE OTHE "Other crazy stuff that is nothing to do with HDP"

My famous website "The Other Realm" is at:
http://www.geocities.com/hollywood/7440/contents.htm

It was originally gonna be just about Amiga but got quite bored. Its now 
about loadsa stuff.  It became quite popular quite quickly, which was quite 
strange because it was quite stupid at the beginning.  After I changed quite 
a few things in the appearance of it the counter rocketed up quite quickly, 
which was quite nice. Quite shortly after that, a guy called Alan Miller 
modfied the Amiga Pages and he made a "The Other Realm" title picture thingy 
which is now the official logo.

Yes I know you`re wondering why I used the word "quite" quite a lot of times.
Well, I`ll tell you a story about it:

It all started when I was really little, about 3, and I was really small, and I 
was really young and really stupid. I didn`t really know much really. Anyway
a few years later, well actually about 5 years later really, I had a really
strange vision which really worried me. In my vision, a really weird looking
monster came up to me and said "Really Pete, when you`re older you will use
the word `quite` a lot, when you write an Amigaguide."  After that I felt really
tired so I went to sleep on my really comfortable bed. When I woke up of course
I didn`t really feel tired any more really.  Which, really, I suppose makes
sense, doesn`t it, really.

Yes I know you`re wondering why I used the word "really" quite a lot of times.
Well I`ll tell you another story etc... :

